{"tid":1748051,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"城大：高層收到情報校園將成下一示威地方，會封鎖校園","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:04:22.000Z","uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"155725690eb4345c6a1ae010101cbd538cfaef5f","tid":1748051,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"城大公告指有訊息顯示將成下一個出現各種形式示威地點<br />\n<br />\n城大向全體教職員及學生發出公告，表示來自多個可靠渠道的訊息顯示，城大將成下一個出現各種形式示威的地方，可能危害教職員和學生的安全，以及令大學校園遭受進一步破壞及影響復修工作。城大又說，校園近日遭受前所未有的破壞，因此希望師生理解和合作，校方必須實施多項措施，包括提升物業和保安管理、暫時關閉校園等。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-23 20:55:21"},{"pid":"fe98b41dde9ef1c9ea3a535de13cbfce8dd18627","tid":1748051,"uid":165749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"永久關閉？"},{"pid":"775506d7cc2583bd971cc0120af01188d877b775","tid":1748051,"uid":214192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:30:32.000Z","msg":"佢哋有被害妄想症<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51cc2bd4b45a6ee986064782f5d9d3915c742f7","tid":1748051,"uid":303473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2935a4f6e68900daf6cac5998c9686a87944b072","tid":1748051,"uid":2247,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"理大都未有你shitty 咁撚串"},{"pid":"e9f1b49be46aabe63642d99614d51cf5014edef3","tid":1748051,"uid":281020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"請政府宣佈封港<br />\n全香港都有可能成為示威地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b394640a97eb77ed3f48add015949260c8fb56ef","tid":1748051,"uid":1807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"封埋廣播道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41